title: Janis Ian Collection-10 albums EAC FLAC
description:
Ten albums from Janis Ian spanning Society's Child from the 1960's to a double live album from 2003. 

The masterpiece is of course 1975's Between the Lines. The version here is the very rare Japanese Gold Disk version remastered by Kevin Gray (from Audio Fidelity), that made my other three CD versions of this album (especially an early Columbia version) sound dull, hissy and insipid. My 1970's LP pressing was close to this Gold Disk, but didn't quite match it. 

The other albums include Night Rains, Stars, Billie's Bones, Hunger, Revenge, Live-Without a Net and Unreleased 2
